\c 1
\s Kutambudzika kwevaIsraeri paEgipita
\p
\v 1 Zvino awa mazita evanakomana vaIsraeri vakasvika kuEgipita naJakove: murume umwe neumwe neimba yake:
\v 2 Rubheni, Simioni, Revhi, naJudha,
\v 3 Isaskari, Zebhuruni, naBhenjamini,
\v 4 Dhani, naNafutari, Gadhi, naAsheri.
\v 5 Zvino mweya yese yakabva muchiuno chaJakove yakange iri mweya makumi manomwe; asi Josefa wakange a\add to\add*va muEgipita.
\v 6 Zvino Josefa wakafa, nevana vababa vake vese, nezera rese iro.
\v 7 Zvino vana vaIsraeri vakaberekana, ndokuwanda kwazvo, vakapamhidzirwa, vakava nesimba kwazvo; nyika ndokuzadzwa navo.
\p
\v 8 Zvino pakamuka mambo mutsva pamusoro peEgipita, wakange asingaziva Josefa.
\v 9 Iye ndokuti kuvanhu vake: Tarirai, rudzi rwevana vaIsraeri, rwakawanda uye vakasimba kutipfuura.
\v 10 Uyai, ngativangwarire, zvimwe vangawanda, ndokuitika kuti kana kukava nehondo, vangabatana nevavengi vedu ndokutirwisa, ndokukwira vachibva munyika ino.
\v 11 Naizvozvo vakagadza pamusoro pavo vatariri vebasa, kuti vavanetse nemitoro yavo. Uye vakavakira Farao maguta ane matura, Pitomi naRaamesesi.
\v 12 Asi pavaivanetsa, ndipo pavaiwanda ndokukura, zvino vakarwadziwa nekuda kwevana vaIsraeri.
\v 13 Zvino vaEgipita vakabatisa vana vaIsraeri neutsinye,
\v 14 ndokurwadzisa upenyu hwavo neutapwa hwakaoma, pamatope nepazvitina, nepakubata kwese mumunda, nekubata kwavo kwese kwavaivabatisa neutsinye.
\p
\v 15 Zvino mambo weEgipita wakataura nananyamukuta vevaHebheru, avo zita reumwe raiva Shifira, uye zita reumwe Pua;
\v 16 ndokuti: Kana muchiita basa reunyamukuta kuvakadzi vevaHebheru, mukaona pachigaro chekuponera, kana ari mwanakomana ipapo mumuuraye, asi kana ari mwanasikana, ipapo achararama.
\v 17 Asi vananyamukuta vakatya Mwari, uye vakasaita mambo weEgipita sezvaakavaraira asi vakarega vanakomana vari vapenyu.
\v 18 Zvino mambo weEgipita wakadana vananyamukuta, ndokuti kwavari: Maitirei chinhu ichi, mukarega vanakomana vari vapenyu?
\p
\v 19 Vananyamukuta ndokuti kuna Farao: Nokuti vakadzi vevaHebheru havana kuita sevakadzi vevaEgipita, nokuti vane simba; uye vanopona vananyamukuta vasati vasvika kwavari.
\v 20 Naizvozvo Mwari wakaitira vananyamukuta zvakanaka, vanhu ndokuwanda, vakava nesimba kwazvo.
\v 21 Zvino zvakaitika nokuti vananyamukuta vaitya Mwari, kuti wakavavakira misha.
\v 22 Farao ndokuraira vanhu vake vese, achiti: Mwanakomana umwe neumwe unoberekwa mukandire murwizi, asi mwanasikana umwe neumwe murege ari mupenyu.
